                            <item xml:id="a5"><desc type="GuestText"><ref type="work" corresp="LIT3058RepCh338">Ǝsäggǝd läki ǝsäggǝd läki ǝsäggǝd läki wäʾǝweddǝsäki</ref> (“I worship you, I worship you, I worship you and I praise you”, Hymn to the Virgin Mary, Chaine nr. 338). The hymn is written in an inaccurate hand. The refrain of each stanza is rubricated. Incipit:</desc> 
                              <locus from="157vb" to="158vb"/>
                              <q xml:lang="gez">[እ]ሰግድ፡ ለኪ፡ ወ[እ]ዌድስኪ፡ ኦእ ግዝእትየ፡ ቅድስት፡ ድንግል፡ ማርያም፡ ወላዲተ፡ አምላክ፡ በከመ፡ ወደሱኪ፡ ወሰገዱ፡ ለኪ፡ መላእክት፡</q>
